<plot>Paula Perillo is the intrepid, sexy, and tough lead investigative reporter Of the Big City Daily Gazette. She is brilliant and resourceful, joined by sidekick Jimmy Smith, mentored by editor Slim Jackson and rivaled by society beat reporter Veronica Vilencourt. Paula is a growing legend in both the streets, society and the criminal underworld. Her arch-enemy is Anthony Carleoni, who she will stop and bring to justice soon. Despite many drawbacks and constant peril, her spirit cannot be defeated.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?426556</url></doc>
